## 1.2.0
* Port to opam 2.0
* Port to dune
* Port to Lablgtk3
* Support OCaml 4.08.0 (esp. error messages)
* Re-enabled, and improved, automatic completion (Lablgtk3 seems to have fixed it!)
* Removed the font selection dialog (Lablgtk3 seems to no longer bind it; not that it's really important...)
* Some small fixes

## 1.1.5
* Fixes for -safe-string and OCaml 4.06.0

## 1.1.4
* Change build system to jbuilder (and fix linking on recent OCaml)
* Fixed GTK warnings and a segfault

## 1.1.3
* Fixed warnings on init (removed Format redirection code)
* Updated Makefiles for newer ocp-build
* Load .ocamlinit, following ocaml's default behaviour
* Fixed issue with `ocamlrun ocaml` on some distributions

## 1.1.2
* Fixed dependency to the new ocp-indent/index install format
* Install through opam-installer

## 1.1.1
* Updated for latest ocp-index
* Status bar and completion now understand above opens

## 1.1.0
* UI cleanup
* New color themes (dark and light)
* Added a few keyboard shortcuts (fullscreen, switch theme, select font)
* Added automatic library type display in a status-line (using ocp-index)
* A few fixes (OSX font, command-line arguments on Windows, 3.12 compatibility)

## 1.0.1
* Fixed issues #24, #36, #37, #38, #39, mainly related to UI
* Enhanced phrase boundary handling
* Fixed ocaml message coloration
